* mount tmpfs on tmp/. Deal with tmpfs while starting (reinstantiate
  skeleton files on each start). Automount tmpfs if not mounted during
  'omd start'. Handle tmp on 'omd mv' and 'omd cp' and 'omd rm'.

* Lock operations 'start', 'cp', 'mv', 'update', and 'rm' while site is
  up.

* Implement error handling in omd utility.
